# OAuth API v3

## The Brightcove OAuth API

The Brightcove OAuth API allows you authenticate with the Brightcove services to get access to other Brightcove APIs. For most cases, you will only use the API directly to retieve an `access_token`. For more information, see the [OAuth Overview](https://docs.brightcove.com/en/perform/oauth-api/guides/oauth-api-overview.html)

## Base URL

The base URL for the API is:

    https://oauth.brightcove.com/v3

# Group Client Credentials Flow

